      p
        | Get a free pair of
        strong.emphasis &nbsp;Stoned Earphones&nbsp;
        | by referring your friends.  If 10 of them purchase a pair
        | using your unique link, we send you a free pair.  You also get other great rewards along the way.

      a(href='signup').button.claim-link-button
        | CLAIM YOUR LINK

  section#stoned-instagram
    h1 See how others rock.
    #instafeed

  section#share
    .content
      h1 Show us love
      ul.shares
        li
          a#social-facebook(href=social.facebook.shareLink, target='_blank')
            i.fa.fa-facebook-square
        li
          a#social-twitter(href=social.twitter.shareLink, target='_blank')
            i.fa.fa-twitter
        li
          a#social-email(href=social.email.shareLink)
